pageContext.description: Ornamented round socket with 10 concentric parts of circles, there are 10 of these figures (At B), each consists of 5 fine lines and an outside stronger line. In the centre is a punch mark. -6 circles round rivet holes at A. Damaged edges. A wooden shaft remains in good condition.
pageContext.other: Width: blade 22mm; 65mm; socket 30mm,Weight: 480 gms; wooden shaft 45 gms
pageContext.associations: Hoard of leaf-shaped swords, spearheads, ferrules, and rings (53 articles in 63 fragments).
